name: webrtcvad
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "webrtcvad" %}
{% set version = "2.0.10" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/webrtcvad-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f1bed2fb25b63fb7b1a55d64090c993c9c9167b28485ae0bcdd81cf6ede96aea

build:
  number: 3
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  skip: true  # [py<37]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - webrtcvad
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/wiseman/py-webrtcvad
  summary: Python interface to the Google WebRTC Voice Activity Detector (VAD)
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
